thread.title: Baptiste
thread.title_full: Melbourne Watch Company reviewed by Baptiste

author: Baptiste
title: Baptiste
text: The watches are extremely good looking and the quality is always there as well. I've always had a response (in a timely manner!) when enquiring about a product. I bought two watches for myself and one for my partner, always a pleasure to put them on my wrist!
